results.title: Club Advisor
results.description: Our club advisor is leaving! Please come wish her good bye :(

results.title: Membership Forms Due
results.description: If you want to be a member of the Random Club, you must hand in a membership form to an officer by the end of this month. No exceptions will be made.

results.title: New Club Advisor
results.description: We have a new club advisor now! You can visit him at B244 at anytime to catch him up with what the club has been doing so far, and make him feel welcome!

results.title: Membership Forms Due
results.description: If you want to be in the club for the remainder of the year, you must turn in the membership form so we can add you into the system!

results.title: Early Release
results.description: Don't forget, this Friday, school ends at 12:30! The schedule is 4567.

results.title: Report Cards
results.description: Come pick up your report cards in the main office when you can!

results.title: Big Meeting!
results.description: Let's go!! We need to plan all the big events we have coming up, and if you attend, we'll give out T-shirts!

results.title: Thanksgiving Event
results.description: Come to the annual Thanksgiving parade and football game where students and faculty get together for some fun activities!

results.title: Club Picture
results.description: We will be having our club picture taken this meeting, which will be going into this year's yearbook...don't miss it!

results.title: Job Applications
results.description: If you would like to work with the organization that we're partnered with, please contact our club advisor or see him at B337 for more information on the matter. Be sure to bring your student ID card.

results.title: Class Assembly
results.location: (From 9th to 12th) Caf A, Caf B, Gym, Auditorium
results.description: All the classes will meet at a designated location for an hour to discuss plans and events.

results.title: Sports Tournament
results.description: There's nothing more fun than tournaments like these! Come for free and earn prizes.

results.title: Flash Sale!
results.description: We're selling clothing and objects for a discount from our usual prices; it'll run from 2 to 4 PM, so be sure to come see if there's anything you like!
